        {
            "title": "天文台｜早上清涼 日間溫暖及非常乾燥 最高氣溫約25度",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/54ec75b92076ccca4179dfe3e8107304/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040306394760054.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>東北季候風正為廣東沿岸帶來清涼及晴朗的天氣。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日天氣預測，天晴。早上清涼。日間溫暖及非常乾燥，最高氣溫約25度。吹和緩東至東北風。\n\n</p>\n<p>展望清明節大致天晴，日間溫暖及乾燥。週末期間雲量較多，短暫時間有陽光。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174273/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"分區氣溫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/99155ba30dd264d8a7172b4ffd4c7b40/2025-04/2025-04-03_06_26_19.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        分區氣溫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174274/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"九天天氣預報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5dda00ed656b37ec9b4c492ec9eff818/2025-04/2025-04-03_06_26_51.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        九天天氣預報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174275/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日間溫暖及非常乾燥，最高氣溫約25度。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aae7dd8144b88348780f489a10102405/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-06-22-57_003.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間溫暖及非常乾燥，最高氣溫約25度。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174276/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"吹和緩東至東北風。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/56afb0f186ccf0c6a8baf210b71f1115/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-06-22-59_004.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        吹和緩東至東北風。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174277/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"展望清明節大致天晴，日間溫暖及乾燥。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/daa258f724a65a81524e7354428e3be4/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-06-23-02_005.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        展望清明節大致天晴，日間溫暖及乾燥。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>乾燥的偏東氣流會在今明兩日影響廣東沿岸，該區普遍晴朗，日間溫暖。而一道雲帶會在接近週末至下週初覆蓋南海北部及廣東沿岸，該區有幾陣驟雨。預料下週中期廣東地區風勢微弱，日間相當溫暖，早晚沿岸有薄霧。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
