        {
            "title": "銅鑼灣住宅單位疑雪櫃起火 消防救出女住戶及兩狗 清醒送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"女戶住連同兩犬被送往醫院治理。黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b7fdce1651e2e093e854653b6ed6fc95/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040306051078699.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">女戶住連同兩犬被送往醫院治理。黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>銅鑼灣發生火警。今日（3日）凌晨3時許，當局一名女子接獲報案，指其永興街9-11號住宅單位內，有雪櫃冒煙起火，女事主及愛犬被困單位內。\n\n</p>\n<p>消防接報到場，動用一條喉及一隊煙帽隊灌救，並於單位內連人帶犬救出。女事主吸入濃煙不適，連同兩隻愛犬同送院治理。消防正調查起火原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174268/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女戶主清理送院治理。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a1e6ab2f9e47f97eff8d5961ca5e0ad9/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-04-53-20_014.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女戶主清理送院治理。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174264/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防到場將火救熄。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/326ab6dc1115eea06a73655f836f2a54/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-04-52-24_001.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防到場將火救熄。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174265/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"單位外牆熏黑。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5c120d12f9954d5f2bffaeaa02df5070/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-04-52-33_004.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單位外牆熏黑。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174266/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"約 30人疏散至安全位置。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b8d3c05fa70a6722aac8fb9d1c072b71/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-04-52-42_008.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        約 30人疏散至安全位置。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174267/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"約 30人疏散至安全位置。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c70183415ddf212534ece5d8c7fe66c8/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-03-04-53-06_010.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        約 30人疏散至安全位置。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>涉事單位外牆熏黑，約30人疏散至安全位置。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2061810/即時-港聞-銅鑼灣住宅單位疑雪櫃起火-消防救出女住戶及兩狗-清醒送院",
